==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun2|'''brownout'''|'''brownouts'''}}
Also: brown-out, brown out
# Temporary dimming of vision, usually with a brown hue and accompanied by loss of peripheral vision or tunnel vision.

===Verb===
'''to brownout'''

# To experience a partial loss of vision having the characterisics of a brownout, to suffer a brownout.

Also: to brown-out, ..to brown out.
